<div class='questionText'>
<a href="/questions/1719611-forget-shelly-forget-everyone-in-the">Forget Shelly, forget everyone in the household telling others to leave, why the flippin&#39; heck didn&#39;t the daughters do something? Tell the police, priest, school counselor? They didn&#39;t because the abuse shifted? Knowing right from wrong, and how all this was wrong, how could those two daughters do nothing.at.all? I know they&#39;re reading here anxious for responses, pity, whatever, no, these deaths are their faults too.</a>
</div>
