              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer9900462211878044230"><strong>Talk about dysfunctional families!</strong><br/><br/>Unbelievably sadistic, psychopathic mother. Weak, submissive husband. Three abused daughters. Three tortured, murdered &quot;boarders&quot;. Another true crime horror story by Gregg Olsen. He&apos;s not the best writer. Repetitive and illogical reiteration of a cult-like group of inadequate, two dimensional characters who never come alive on the page. Disappointing.</span>
